The KPI shows probability for an end-user to be successfully provided with a service that are carried by E-RABs included in initial context setup procedure. The success rate E-RAB establishment depends on the successful establishment of the RRC connection and S1 signalling between the RBS and the Mobile Management Entity (MME). Hence, the formula is RRC establishment success rate x S1-Sig stablishment success rate x Initial E-RAB setup success rate

The KPI shows how often an end-user abnormally looses an E-RAB during the time the E-RAB is used. It is defined to exclude the impact of traffic model and keep-alive settings for UEs in RRC connected state. The measured drops is normalized with the UE active time.
